      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of exceptional caliber, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This specimen exhibits a level of preservation rarely encountered on the secondary market, retaining its original showroom luster and mechanical precision. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, affirms its status as an investment-grade acquisition. We invite the discerning buyer to secure a motorcar that transcends the standard definition of pre-owned.",
