    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. I have absolutely babied this car from day one, and it's still in total showroom condition\u2014not a single scratch or smudge to be found! It drives like an absolute dream and honestly feels like it just rolled off the lot. I'm really looking for a great new home for it where it'll be just as loved. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
