      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine E92 M3, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L V8 with an 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This unit remains in concours condition, retaining its factory-original carbon fiber roof and flawless Jerez Black finish. Mechanically, the high-pressure double-VANOS system operates perfectly within factory tolerances, and the six-speed manual gearbox offers crisp, short-throw engagement. The chassis benefits from Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and shows zero signs of subframe fatigue or bushing wear. Meticulously maintained with a comprehensive service dossier, this is a collector-grade example of BMW\u2019s high-revving peak.",
      "price": 44950.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Full service history. Professional inspection welcome.",
      "price": 42500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
