    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle is a testament to meticulous ownership. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin retains its original factory scent; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and free of any wear or creasing. Every electronic component, from the high-resolution infotainment system to the climate-controlled seating, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documented exclusively at authorized dealerships. It has been strictly garaged, never seen inclement weather, and driven only on fair-weather weekends. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. No scratches, no dents, and a spotless undercarriage.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
